import React from 'react' import Header from '../layout/Header' import Contents from '../layout/Contents' import Footer from '../layout/Footer' import Title from '../layout/Title' import Contact from '../layout/Contact' import MovieCont from '../includes/MovieCont' function Movie() { const [videos, setVideos] =useState([]); useEffect(()=>{ let requestOptions ={ method:"GET", redirect:"follow", } fetch("https://api.themoviedb.org/3/movie/550?api_key={api}", requestOptions) .then((response) => response.json()) .then((result) => {setVideos(result.items);}) .catch((error) => console.log("error", error)); }); return ( <>
<section className='movie__cont'> <div className='movie__inner'> <MovieList videos={videos}/> </div> </section> <MovieCont/> <Contact/> </Contents> <Footer/> </> ) } export default Movie
